leland North Province|Matabeleland North]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|Jini|Ntuta}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland North Province|Matabeleland North]]\n|Died 19 November 1984.\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|John|Nkomo}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland North Province|Matabeleland North]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|Daniel|Ngwenya}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland North Province|Matabeleland North]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|Ruth|Chinamano}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland North Province|Matabeleland North]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|Jane|Ngwenya}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland North Province|Matabeleland North]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|Thenjiwe|Lesabe}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland North Province|Matabeleland North]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|George|Silundika}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland South Province|Matabeleland South]]\n|Died 9 April 1981.\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|Stephen|Nkomo}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland South Province|Matabeleland South]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|Edward|Ndlovu}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland South Province|Matabeleland South]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|Boyson|Mguni}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland South Province|Matabeleland South]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|Callistus|Ndlovu}}\n| style=\"background:#010100;\" |\n|[[Zimbabwe African People's Union|ZAPU\u2013PF]]\n|[[Matabeleland South Province|Matabeleland South]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|{{Sn|Peter|